Version 0.6-unreleased
======================

* Added an option for output file creation.

* Removed random event term mode (-r).

* Code refactoring towards more efficient data structures.

* added scripts to use LCOV (`http://ltp.sourceforge.net/coverage/lcov.php')
  to determine test case coverage (use `make cover' in `tests' directory)

* Added test cases.

Version 0.5
===========

* First public beta version of Linda.



